      <title>C&amp;C++语法积累</title>
      <link href="/2022/02/25/C&amp;C++%E8%AF%AD%E6%B3%95%E7%A7%AF%E7%B4%AF/"/>
      <url>/2022/02/25/C&amp;C++%E8%AF%AD%E6%B3%95%E7%A7%AF%E7%B4%AF/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="C-重载">C++重载</h2><ul><li>运算符重载</li></ul><h2 id="CMake">CMake</h2><p><a href="https://blog.csdn.net/afei__/article/details/81201039">CMakeLists.txt 语法介绍与实例演练_阿飞的博客-CSDN博客_cmakelist</a></p><h2 id="cin-cout格式控制（未掌握）"><a href="https://blog.csdn.net/tjunxin/article/details/8163635?ops_request_misc=%257B%2522request%255Fid%2522%253A%2522163255684016780262585140%2522%252C%2522scm%2522%253A%252220140713.130102334.pc%255Fall.%2522%257D&amp;request_id=163255684016780262585140&amp;biz_id=0&amp;utm_medium=distribute.pc_search_result.none-task-blog-2~all~first_rank_ecpm_v1~rank_v31_ecpm-2-8163635.pc_search_ecpm_flag&amp;utm_term=cout%E9%87%8C%E6%A0%BC%E5%BC%8F%E6%8E%A7%E5%88%B6%25.1f&amp;spm=1018.2226.3001.4187">cin&amp;cout格式控制（未掌握）</a></h2><p>添加iomanip头文件</p><p>ios::dec  以10进制表示整数<br>ios::hex  以16进制表示整数<br>ios::oct  以8进制表示整数 　<br>setfill(<em>) 设填充字符为</em>　　<br>setprecision(n) 设显示精度为n位 　　<br>setw(n) 设域宽为n个字符 　　<br>setiosflags(ios::fixed) 固定的浮点显示 　　<br>setiosflags(ios::scientific) 指数表示 　　<br>setiosflags(ios::left) 左对齐 　　<br>setiosflags(ios::right) 右对齐 　　<br>setiosflags(ios::skipws) 忽略前导空白 　　<br>setiosflags(ios::uppercase)16进制数大写输出 　　<br>setiosflags(ios::lowercase)16进制数小写输出<br>ios::dec  以10进制表示整数<br>ios::hex  以16进制表示整数<br>ios::oct  以8进制表示整数<br>ios::showbase  为整数添加一个表示其进制的前缀<br>ios::internal  在符号位和数值的中间插入需要数量的填充字符以使串两端对齐<br>ios::left  在串的末尾插入填充字符以使串居左对齐<br>ios::right  在串的前面插入填充字符以使串居右对齐<br>ios::boolalpha  将bool类型的值以true或flase表示，而不是1或0<br>ios::fixed  将符点数按照普通定点格式处理（非科学计数法）<br>ios::scientific  将符点数按照科学计数法处理（带指数域）<br>ios::showpoint  在浮点数表示的小数中强制插入小数点（默认情况是浮点数表示的整数不显示小数点）<br>ios::showpos  强制在正数前添加+号<br>ios::skipws  忽略前导的空格（主要用于输入流，如cin）<br>ios::unitbuf  在插入（每次输出）操作后清空缓存<br>ios::uppercase  强制大写字母</p><p>例如：</p><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cout.<span class="built_in">setf</span>(ios::fixed);</span><br><span class="line">cout &lt;&lt; fixed&lt;&lt;<span class="built_in">setprecision</span>(<span class="number">4</span>) &lt;&lt; <span class="number">9.888383322</span> &lt;&lt; endl;<span class="comment">//输出小数点后4位</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="STL和基本的数据结构">STL和基本的数据结构</h2><ul><li><p><strong>通用操作</strong></p><table><thead><tr><th style="text-align:left">操作</th><th>描述</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td style="text-align:left">X u;</td><td>创建名为u，类型为X的空对象</td></tr><tr><td style="text-align:left">X(a);</td><td>创建对象x的拷贝</td></tr><tr><td style="text-align:left">X u(a); 或  X u = a;</td><td>u是a的拷贝（复制构造函数）</td></tr><tr><td style="text-align:left">r = a;</td><td>r等于a(复制赋值)</td></tr><tr><td style="text-align:left">X u(rv);或 X u = rv;</td><td>u等于rv的原始值（移动构造函数）</td></tr><tr><td style="text-align:left">(&amp;a) -&gt; ~X();</td><td>对a的每个元素执行析构函数</td></tr><tr><td style="text-align:left">begin()</td><td>返回指向首元素的迭代器</td></tr><tr><td style="text-align:left">end()</td><td>返回指向超尾元素的迭代器</td></tr><tr><td style="text-align:left">cbegin()</td><td>返回指向首元素的const迭代器</td></tr><tr><td style="text-align:left">cend()</td><td>返回指向<strong>超尾</strong>元素的const迭代器</td></tr><tr><td style="text-align:left">size()</td><td>返回元素数目</td></tr><tr><td style="text-align:left">maxsize()</td><td>返回容器最大可能长度</td></tr><tr><td style="text-align:left">empty()</td><td>判断容器是否为空</td></tr><tr><td style="text-align:left">swap()</td><td>交换两个容器的内容</td></tr><tr><td style="text-align:left">==</td><td>若两个容器<strong>长度相同、元素相同、元素顺序相同</strong>则为真</td></tr><tr><td style="text-align:left">!=</td><td>上述的反</td></tr></tbody></table><p>双向或随机迭代器的容器（vector, map, list, set, array, deque）是可反转的，则会提供可反转容器的操作<br>（类似于尾指针的操作）</p><table><thead><tr><th>操作</th><th>描述</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>X::reverse_iterator</td><td>指向类型T的反向迭代器</td></tr><tr><td>X::const_reverse_iterator</td><td>指向类型T的const反向迭代器</td></tr><tr><td>a.rbegin()</td><td>返回指向a的<strong>超尾</strong>的反向迭代器</td></tr><tr><td>a.rend()</td><td>返回指向a的<strong>首元素</strong>的反向迭代器</td></tr><tr><td>a.crbegin()</td><td>返回指向a的超尾的const反向迭代器</td></tr><tr><td>a.crend()</td><td>返回指向a的首元素的const反向迭代器</td></tr></tbody></table><p><strong>更具体地内容请见C++ Primer Plus 附录G，需要默写</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>顺序式</strong></p><ul><li><a href="#array">array</a></li><li><a href="#vector">vector</a></li><li><a href="#list">list</a></li><li><a href="#deque">deque</a></li><li><a href="#queue">queue</a></li><li><a href="#priority_queue">priority_queue</a></li><li><a href="#stack">stack</a></li></ul></li><li><p>关联式</p><ul><li><a href="#set">set</a></li><li><a href="#multiset">multiset</a></li><li><a href="#map">map</a></li><li><a href="#mulrimap">multimap</a></li></ul></li><li><h2 id="array">array</h2><p>长度固定，使用静态（栈）内存，效率更高</p></li><li><h2 id="vector">vector</h2><p>空间足够就用静态数组，空间紧张就用vector<br>从末尾能快速插入或删除，直接访问任何元素</p><ul><li>声明：</li></ul><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">//int型</span></span><br><span class="line">vector&lt; <span class="type">int</span> &gt; a;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="function">vector&lt; <span class="type">int</span> &gt; <span class="title">b</span><span class="params">(a)</span></span>; <span class="comment">//用a定義b</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function">vector&lt; <span class="type">int</span> &gt; <span class="title">a</span><span class="params">(<span class="number">100</span>)</span></span>;<span class="comment">//a有100个值为0的元素</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function">vector&lt; <span class="type">int</span> &gt; <span class="title">a</span><span class="params">(<span class="number">100</span>,<span class="number">6</span>)</span></span>;<span class="comment">//a有100个值为6的元素</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//string型</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function">vector&lt; string &gt; <span class="title">a</span><span class="params">(<span class="number">10</span>,<span class="string">&quot;null&quot;</span>)</span></span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="function">vector&lt; string &gt; <span class="title">vec</span><span class="params">(<span class="number">10</span>,<span class="string">&quot;hello&quot;</span>)</span></span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="function">vector&lt; string &gt; <span class="title">b</span><span class="params">(a.begin(),a.end())</span></span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//结构体型</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">struct</span> <span class="title class_">point</span> &#123; <span class="type">int</span> a, <span class="type">int</span> y; &#125;;</span><br><span class="line">vector &lt; point &gt; a;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//二维</span></span><br><span class="line">vector &lt; <span class="type">int</span> &gt; a[MAXN]; <span class="comment">//一维动态，二维固定</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>操作:</li></ul><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">a.<span class="built_in">push_back</span>(<span class="number">100</span>);</span><br><span class="line">a.<span class="built_in">pop_back</span>();</span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">int</span> size = a.<span class="built_in">size</span>();</span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">bool</span> isEmpty = a.<span class="built_in">empty</span>();</span><br><span class="line">a.<span class="built_in">insert</span>(a.<span class="built_in">begin</span>()+i,k);</span><br><span class="line">a.<span class="built_in">insert</span>(a.<span class="built_in">end</span>(),<span class="number">10</span>,<span class="number">5</span>);<span class="comment">//尾部插入10个值为5的元素</span></span><br><span class="line">a.<span class="built_in">erase</span>(a,<span class="built_in">begin</span>()+<span class="number">2</span>);<span class="comment">//删除第3个元素</span></span><br><span class="line">a.<span class="built_in">erase</span>(a.<span class="built_in">begin</span>()+i,a.<span class="built_in">begin</span>()+j);<span class="comment">//删除[i,j-1]的元素</span></span><br><span class="line">a.<span class="built_in">resize</span>(n);<span class="comment">//重置数组大小,若n&gt;size,多出的置0;若n&lt;size,则删除多出的元素</span></span><br><span class="line">a.<span class="built_in">clear</span>();</span><br><span class="line">a.<span class="built_in">reverse</span>(a.<span class="built_in">begin</span>(),a.<span class="built_in">end</span>());</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">sort</span>(a.<span class="built_in">begin</span>(),a.<span class="built_in">end</span>());</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><h2 id="stack">stack</h2><p>​FILO</p><ul><li>声明：</li></ul><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">include</span> <span class="string">&lt;stack&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line">stack &lt; Type &gt; s;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>操作：</li></ul><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">s.<span class="built_in">push</span>(item);</span><br><span class="line">s.<span class="built_in">top</span>();</span><br><span class="line">s.<span class="built_in">pop</span>();</span><br><span class="line">s.<span class="built_in">size</span>();</span><br><span class="line">s.<span class="built_in">empty</span>();</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><h2 id="queue">queue</h2><p>​FIFO</p><ul><li>声明：</li></ul><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">include</span> <span class="string">&lt;queue&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line">queue&lt; Type &gt; q;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>操作：</li></ul><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">q.<span class="built_in">push</span>(item);</span><br><span class="line">q.<span class="built_in">pop</span>();</span><br><span class="line">q.<span class="built_in">front</span>();</span><br><span class="line">q.<span class="built_in">back</span>();<span class="comment">//队尾</span></span><br><span class="line">q.<span class="built_in">size</span>();</span><br><span class="line">q.<span class="built_in">empty</span>();</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><h2 id="priority-queue">priority_queue</h2><p>优先队列，是队列与排序的完美结合，每次的push和pop都会根据优先级动态调整元素<br>使用二叉堆实现的，push和pop的复杂度为$$ log_2^n$$</p><ul><li>声明：</li></ul><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">include</span> <span class="string">&lt;queue&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line">priority_queue&lt;<span class="type">int</span>&gt; a; <span class="comment">//默认大根堆</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//等同于 priority_queue&lt;int, vector&lt;int&gt;, less&lt;int&gt; &gt; a;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>操作：</li></ul><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">q.<span class="built_in">push</span>(item);</span><br><span class="line">q.<span class="built_in">pop</span>();</span><br><span class="line">q.<span class="built_in">top</span>();<span class="comment">//返回最高优先级的元素</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><h2 id="list">list</h2><p>双向链表，内存空间不连续，通过指针访问，插入删除都是O（1）的。</p><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">list&lt; <span class="type">int</span> &gt; mylist;</span><br><span class="line">list&lt; <span class="type">int</span> &gt; ::iterator it;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span>(<span class="type">int</span> i = <span class="number">1</span> ;i &lt;= n; i++)  </span><br><span class="line">    mylist.<span class="built_in">push_back</span>(i);  <span class="comment">//赋值for(it = mylist.begin(); it != mylist; it++; ) cout &lt;&lt; *it; // 访问</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><h2 id="set">set</h2><p>集合<br><strong>使用二叉搜索树实现，每个元素只出现一次，且是排好序的</strong>,<strong>但访问速度是</strong>$$O(log_2^n)$$</p><ul><li>声明：</li></ul><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">include</span><span class="string">&lt; list &gt;</span>set <span class="string">&lt; Type &gt;</span> A;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>操作：</li></ul><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">A.<span class="built_in">insert</span>(item);</span><br><span class="line">A.<span class="built_in">erase</span>(item);</span><br><span class="line">A.<span class="built_in">clear</span>();</span><br><span class="line">A.<span class="built_in">empty</span>();</span><br><span class="line">A.<span class="built_in">size</span>();</span><br><span class="line">A.<span class="built_in">find</span>(k);<span class="comment">//返回一个指向k的迭代器A.lower_bound(k);//返回指向第一个不小于k的元素的迭代器A.upper_bound(k);</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><h2 id="map">map</h2><p><strong>使用平衡二叉搜索树实现，键（key）与值（value）一一对应</strong></p><ul><li>声明：</li></ul><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">include</span> <span class="string">&lt;map&gt;</span>map <span class="string">&lt; Type &gt;</span> A;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>操作：</li></ul><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">A.<span class="built_in">insert</span>(item);</span><br><span class="line">A.<span class="built_in">erase</span>(item);</span><br><span class="line">A.<span class="built_in">clear</span>();</span><br><span class="line">A.<span class="built_in">empty</span>();</span><br><span class="line">A.<span class="built_in">size</span>();</span><br><span class="line">A.<span class="built_in">find</span>(k);<span class="comment">//返回一个指向k的迭代器A.lower_bound(k);//返回指向第一个不小于k的元素的迭代器A.upper_bound(k);</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><h1>STL函数：</h1></li></ul><ol><li><a href="#sort">sort</a><br>2. <a href="#next_permutation">next_permutation</a></li></ol>]]></content>
      
      
      
